# =============================================================================
# DGGS Benchmark Replication - Central Configuration
# =============================================================================
#
# This file defines key versions and settings used across the project.
# Edit THIS FILE to update versions - all other files reference this.
#
# Usage:
#   - Docker:         docker build --build-arg CONFIG_FILE=config.env .
